snippet.title: Diana and Roma Entertainment for kids at the hotel
snippet.description:
Diana and Roma have fun at the Nirvana Dolce Vita Hotel in Turkey. Kids show that at the resort you need to take a break from gadgets and spend time playing in the kids club, water park, playground, and also visit the children's disco.
Thanks for watching!
